description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Stroganoff Pies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken Stroganoff Pies Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 650 g chicken breast stir fry strips

recipeInstructions.text: Divide stroganoff mixture between dishes. Top each with a pastry lid and return to oven for 5 minutes until heated through. Serve with salad leaves.
